code: public static HazelcastOperation getHazelcastOperation(String name) {     if (name == null) {         return null.     }     for (HazelcastOperation hazelcastOperation : values) {         if (hazelcastOperation.toString().equalsIgnoreCase(name) || hazelcastOperation.name().equalsIgnoreCase(name)) {             return hazelcastOperation.         }     }     throw new IllegalArgumentException(String.format("Operation '%s' is not supported by this component.", name)). }
